import {
    Navbar,
    NavDropdown,
    Container,
    Nav,
    Form,
    Button
  } from "react-bootstrap";
  

function CollapsibleExample() {
    return (
        
      <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark" >
        <Container>
          <Navbar.Brand href="#home">IHRD Malappuram</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
          <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
            <Nav className="me-auto">
            <Nav.Link href="http://casmalappuram.ihrd.ac.in/cas/">
                Home
              </Nav.Link>
              <NavDropdown title="Institution" id="navbarScrollingDropdown">
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action3">History</NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action4">Campus </NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action5">Principal</NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action3">Management</NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action3">
                  Administration
                </NavDropdown.Item>
              </NavDropdown>



             



            </Nav             >
            
            
        
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>
            
  
    );
  }
  
  export default CollapsibleExample;
